OL,5, The mother of a man accused of helping 
OL,6, a gunman who shot a council worker has 
OL,7, told a prosecutor to "prove" she has   
OL,8, lied to a court.                       
OL,10,FLiverpool Crown Court has heard Joseph 
OL,11,FPeers, 29, was allegedly the getaway   
OL,12,Fdriver for James Witham, who has       
OL,13,Fadmitted shooting Ashley Dale in Old   
OL,14,FSwan, Liverpool, in August 2022.       
OL,16,FHis mother Lesley McMahon told the jury
OL,17,Fher son was at home at the time.       
OL,19,FAccused of lying by prosecutor Paul    
OL,20,FGreaney KC, she said: "You prove that".
